Description: Vietnamese input method (Telex) for Fcitx5
 fcitx5-vnkey is a Vietnamese input method engine for the Fcitx5
 input method framework. It supports the Telex typing method with
 full NFC precomposed Unicode output.
 .
 The engine core is a standalone C++23 library with no Fcitx5
 dependency, making it fully unit-testable, with a thin Fcitx5
 addon layer on top.
